 Successful completion of the proposed clinical trial will increase our understanding of the safety, efficacy and underlying mechanisms of selective immunotherapy with the anti-CD3 monoclonal antibody hOKT3gamma1 (Ala-ala) for the maximization of engraftment and functional survival of allogeneic human islets in surgical and type 1 diabetic recipients.

